++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
+                             quick instruction                              +
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
This file provided that you have successfully installed the projects
applications under phpgroupware and can access the "Projects" menu
page including p*hours-, p*statistics-, p*delivery- and p*billing-links.  

The main page contains a ADD button to create projects and a
ACTIVITY LIST button. 
First you have to create your activities. Activities meens global categories
of your work into you have to sort your jobs. They regulate the hours 
per workunit and the bill per workunit for each job.  

than you can create your projects and assign activities to them.   
You can choose the type of activity: bookable(no invoice) or billable.
The projecthours app manages your daily jobs. You can only submit a job to a
project, if there are activities avaiable.  

If you want to create invoices or deliveries you have to select a customer
before. 
Change the logo.gif in p*billing dir with yours or remove it if you don't
want a logo in your invoices or deliveries.

You have to create a group 'projectAdmin'. Each member of this group is
able to modify or delete all projects data.
The project - coordinator is the chosen primary employee and authorized 
to modify his project.   

grtx
